ss="prva kekl">The user must have an open user account at the S Dream Internet Store.</li><ul style="float: left;padding-left: 46px;"><li>The user must enter his exact phone number</li><li>The user must enter his exact billing information (this information from S Dream Store sends the Commercial Bank to validate your card, therefore the data must be the same as on the card)</li><li>If a user has a different delivery address, he / she needs to create 2 addresses, so that he / she can indicate which address is for delivery, and which is used for billing adress. If you need help with adding a new address, click the "Learn more" button.<a href="https://www.sdream.rs/en/info/how-to-add-new-addresses/" class="button btn btn-default button-medium">Learn more</a></li></ul><li class="druga kekl" style=" width: 100%; ">Delivery of goods is only possible on the territory of the Republic of Serbia, at your address or in S Dream retail facilities.</li><li class="treca kekl">Only the payment card owner can make a payment.</li></ol><p style=" float: left; width: 100%;" class="kekl">Online credit card payment procedure</p><div style="float: left;"><div style="width:100%;position:;"><figure style=" width: 100%;"><img title="Zaštićena stranica za naplatu Komercijalne banke" alt="Zaštićena stranica za naplatu Komercijalne banke" src="https://sdream.rs/img/odabirNacinaPlacanja.jpg" style="margin: 0;width: 100%;"> <figcaption style=" font-weight: 900; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px; padding-top: 2px;">Figure 1 - Choosing a payment method</figcaption></figure></div><div style="margin-bottom:16px"><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">At the very end of the order, you will be taken to a step to choose a payment method. When you choose to pay by credit card, you will be redirected to the "Order review" page.</p></div></div><div><div class="levko"><figure><img title="Zaštićena stranica za naplatu Komercijalne banke" alt="Zaštićena stranica za naplatu Komercijaln