nd checking is performed exclusively between card and bank users, while S Dream Web Store does not have access to data that is exchanged.</p></div></div><div style="float: left;width: 100%;"><div style="width: 100%;float: left;"><figure style=" width: 100%;"><img title="Informacije na karticama" alt="Informacije na karticama" src="https://sdream.rs/img/kartice.jpg" style="margin: 0;border: 2px solid #f16323;border-radius: 4px;padding: 16px;width: 100%;"> <figcaption style=" font-weight: 900; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px; padding-top: 2px;">Figure 4 - Payment card parameters</figcaption></figure></div></div><div style=" float: left;"><div class="levko"><figure><img title="Primer 3D secure stranice Telenor banke" alt="Primer 3D secure stranice Telenor banke" src="https://sdream.rs/img/vbv2.jpg" style="margin: 0;border: 2px solid #f16323;border-radius: 4px;width: 100%;"> <figcaption style=" font-weight: 900; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px; padding-top: 2px;">Figure 5 - 3D Secure webpage</figcaption></figure></div><div class="desko"><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">After entering your parameters from the card you will be redirected to 3D secure validation.</p><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">f your card supports 3D secure validation, how it can be activated and how it is implemented, you can check with your card issuer's bank. If your card does not have the 3D validation option, you can make payments in the usual way without this additional step.</p><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">For safer Internet shopping, Komercijalna Banka supports Verified by Visa and MasterCard Secure code protection (3D Secure card verification). 3D Secure is an international standard that is used to check card users and provide added security during online shopping. The service helps protect against unauthorized use of the card by third parties during the implementation of Internet transactions.</p><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">3D Secure implies that when online payments, the card user confirms his identity by using a secret password received by the bank via SMS or e-mail, which reduces the possibility of abuse - similar to the use of a PIN at the ATM. In some cases, you can get a portable reader for generating a password from a bank.</p></div></div><div style=" float: left;"><div class="levko"><figure><img title="Uspešna porudžbina" alt="Uspešna porudžbina" src="https://sdream.rs/img/uspesnaPorudzbina.jpg" style="margin: 0;border: 2px solid #f16323;border-radius: 4px;width: 100%;"> <figcaption style=" font-weight: 900; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px; padding-top: 2px;">Figure 6 - Successful order</figcaption></figure></div><div class="desko"><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">After the successful payment, you will be redirected to the "Order review" page and order will automaticly be completed.</p><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">If the payment was not successful, you would also be redirected to the "Order review" page, which will get a response from the bank (why the transaction is not executed). "</p></div></div><div style="float: left;width: 100%;"><div style="width:100%"><figure style=" width: 100%;"><img title="Potvrđivanje porudžbine" alt="Potvrđivanje porudžbine" src="https://sdream.rs/img/potvrdjivanjeporudzbine.jpg" style="margin: 0;border: 2px solid #f16323;border-radius: 4px;width: 100%;"> <figcaption style=" font-weight: 900; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px; padding-top: 2px;">Figure 6 - Successful order confirmation</figcaption></figure></div><div class="width:100%"><p style=" font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">At the very end, you will receive a confirmation from the S Dream Internet Store that your order is successful. You will also receive an email with details of the order.</p></div></div><div style=" float: left; display: block; width: 100%; margin-top: 32px;" class="n